        <h1 class="puppyTitle">About Sheepadoodles</h1>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row puppyTitleRow">
    <p class="dogDescription">What exactly are sheepadoodles? A sheepadoodle is a cross between the Standard Poodle and the Old English Sheepdog. Sheepadoodles are great family dogs. They are very playful, energetic, and friendly dogs. They shed very little, making them great indoor dogs. Sheepadoodles also tend to get along with other dogs very well! They are very intelligent and extremely expressive dogs, making them the perfect pet!</p>
</div>

