    </div>
</div>
<div class="row puppyTitleRow">
    <p class="dogDescription">So you are thinking about bringing a Sheepadoodle into your family! In order to start the process of purchasing a puppy, you will need to first click on the "Contact" link at the top of the page. We will need to gather some information from you. Tell us about your family and other pets! How soon are you able to adopt? Do you live in an apartment? What exactly are you looking for in a dog? We will get back to you with an email including a link for you to pay your deposit. This deposit is non-refundable and and will be deducted from the total price ($1600) upon purchase. Your deposit will guarantee your puppy until the purchase date.</p>
